%E1%BB%AB/poem-sfHCqxaQ75Zp7Waf7a2TsA">Quy khứ lai từ - 歸去來辭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%C3%A1ng-hoa-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-gA5JJaf5Xy6SshvZx4FFWg">Táng hoa từ - 葬花詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/T%C3%A2y-giang-nguy%E1%BB%87t-B%C3%ACnh-S%C6%A1n-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-gyavq9Y7_DhY8sIp9hXRZQ">Tây giang nguyệt - Bình Sơn đường - 西江月－平山堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Vi%E1%BB%85n-bi%E1%BB%87t-ly/poem-chqUZSmoUmFAaHEcI_GANA">Viễn biệt ly - 遠別離</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
